                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t17801018-12-off64" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17801018-12-off64" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801018-12-off64" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silk purse, value 2 d. and a guinea and four shillings in monies, numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17801018-12-victim166" type="victimName">
                           Patrick 
                           Lorder
                        <interp inst="t17801018-12-victim166" type="surname" value="Lorder"></interp>
